

== Interface Overview

The University of Hawaii (UH) will act as the requesting agency and submit annual (and
as needed) requests for refreshes/updates of Medicare Enrollment, Fee-for-Service Claims,
and Encounters data, as well as Medicaid Enrollment, Claims, and Encounters data, to
the CMS Research Data and Assistance Center (ResDAC) at the University of Minnesota
through the State Agency Request Program.

